32
00:01:16,392 --> 00:01:17,703
Sta ancora scappando, huh?

33
00:01:17,704 --> 00:01:19,393
"Il Bag ha ancora la borsa."

34
00:01:19,394 --> 00:01:21,829
"E' a Panama City all'hotel
Fin Del Camino."

35
00:01:21,830 --> 00:01:22,393
