217
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:01,210
Senti, sparisci.

218
00:18:03,285 --> 00:18:05,407
Come andiamo, signori?

219
00:18:09,471 --> 00:18:11,371
Sucre, la pistola.

220
00:18:13,721 --> 00:18:15,621
Forza.

221
00:18:16,846 --> 00:18:18,746
Venite nel vicolo.

